nodes.text: Pash Cracken: An Expanded Universe Character

Pash Cracken: An Expanded Universe Character is a web enhancement written by Cory J. Herndon and released by Wizards of the Coast on November 13, 2003 as a companion to The New Jedi Order: The Final Prophecy. It provides a short biography and stats for Pash Cracken.
